{"lastModified":1772719752416,"uri":"c::17949224288::vessel::3052c4d0-7e8b-11f0-a87c-a1a003b3fcfa","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Dubai, United Arab Emirates\n\nDiscover Matrix, an 82ft Sunseeker yacht refurbished in 2023 to offer a unique blend of luxury and sophistication. With its striking black custom paint and modern design, this yacht is perfect for creating unforgettable memories, whether it’s a corporate gathering, a family outing, or a relaxing day on the water.\n\nThe yacht features expansive living spaces, including a stylish lounge, a refined dining area, and a spacious outdoor deck for alfresco enjoyment. Accommodating up to 30 guests for day charters and 8 overnight, Matrix includes a luxurious master suite with a king-size bed and spa-like ensuite, along with VIP and double cabins, each with private baths. A fully stocked kitchen, bar, and state-of-the-art entertainment systems ensure every detail of your experience is catered for.\n\nPowered by high-performance twin engines, Matrix promises a smooth and comfortable journey. Whether you’re cruising through Dubai Marina, anchoring at the Burj Al Arab, or simply relaxing onboard, this yacht delivers the perfect setting for a memorable day on the water.","blueprint":{"name":"MATRIX","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::3052c4d0-7e8b-11f0-a87c-a1a003b3fcfa::assets::4027bd00-7e8d-11f0-870b-89caa5038b81/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3052c4d0-7e8b-11f0-a87c-a1a003b3fcfa::assets::4028a760-7e8d-11f0-9076-813b2ca5dc1f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3052c4d0-7e8b-11f0-a87c-a1a003b3fcfa::assets::401ce790-7e8d-11f0-8709-89caa5038b81/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3052c4d0-7e8b-11f0-a87c-a1a003b3fcfa::assets::402cc610-7e8d-11f0-870b-89caa5038b81/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3052c4d0-7e8b-11f0-a87c-a1a003b3fcfa::assets::401d5cc0-7e8d-11f0-8709-89caa5038b81/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3052c4d0-7